    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/a01143e5e57e83b58df7cfa508670730.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=72 /></span>你和你的儿时玩伴本来只是在破旧校舍中捡起了一本书，但接下来命运就此出现转折，你们被传送到了一个满是妖怪和邪灵的异次元空间。你们必须想办法逃出此地！在这个超自然维度中，你们遇到了 自称伟大妖怪的伊纲。在这位大妖和香坂姐妹的精神力帮助下，你能否逃离这个诡异的时空呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/000f5445d0b5e7276beb56da9615dc8a.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在如同深邃迷宫的旧校舍钟探索，躲避邪灵，应对诅咒。与看似仁慈的伟大妖怪伊纲结盟，获得特殊能力对抗邪灵！你的不同选择可能通向不同的分支，最终解锁不同的结局，极大增加了游戏的可玩性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/3624864e5c13083b309bd7c930eaaba5.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/28afa29394da1ad07e874616ead13245.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/f4fb8539e9d9ceb18529985a339dfe05.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/dc956c7a3bfdca285e56160c3ca5081a.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/8c5524fe2313878f01d9f855abeec599.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引人入胜的剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过闹鬼的建筑物，探索并推进故事的曲折进展！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多个分支结局</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验自己的行为和选择导致的不同分支，多达五种结局等待你来解锁！</p>",
